This is how unit balance was built.

Units are divided on tanks and dds(damage dealers).
The calculation is that:

dd kills	dd	with 3 hits
dd kills	tank	with 4 hits
tank kills	dd	with 4 hits
tank kills	tank	with 6 hits

Result ratio of damage is 19/25.

TABLE		damage	HP	armor

l.1	tank	9	52	5
	dd	13	36

l.2	tank	11	60	6
	dd	15	44

l.3	tank	13	72	7
	dd	18	52

l.4	tank	15	84	8
	dd	21	60

Non-primary attack damage mostly equal to corresponding level tank damage -10%.

(t - tank, d - damage dealer, h - hybrid, digit - level)
UNITS:
Loyalists:
